Gucci Flora Eau de Toilette - 75 ml (For Women) Price: Rs.3955

Dainty and delicate she is the heart of the house and the perfect lady always charming and helpful. The celebrated fashion house of Gucci adds its signature touch to her tasteful wardrobe with Flora a fragrance so rooted yet heady that wave after wave of floral finesse washes through her. The luxurious perfume seeps into your senses lingering on the edges always while taking you through a bouquet of silken flowers that dance to the lingering tones of Flora. Her gentleness is not to be mistaken for she has all the strength of the contemporary woman suffused into her sultry being.

The Eau de Toilette was designed by the famed Firmenich and launched in the summer of 2009. The floral onslaught starts with the tangy notes of citrus pretty peony and Mandarin orange. The exotic osmanthus adds a whole new dimension to the heart notes along with rose which curl up on a base of soothing sandalwood pensive patchouli and spicy pink pepper adding an edge to Gucci Flora. The champagne-colored elixir is captured in a flacon that is the shape of a hexagon with a bow that adds a sweetly feminine touch to it. Light and airy Gucci Flora is for the woman who knows where she stands and is comfortable with who she is.
